Description: “Engineer Master II Skindiver II” is the second redesigned model that takes its inspiration from the retro divers in the 60’s. The outstanding difference between the first and the second model is the diameter of the case. While the first model was 40.3 mm, this model maintains the original size – 43 mm. The designs of the index and anti-reverse turn bezel also have been upgraded.
